./Issue40/IIIT-Allahabad/IIT2024084/design_notes.txt:4:This design evolves the vintage "Rangara" Bollywood theme into the 2025 "Rangrez" visual identity. It combines the cinematic elements of the 70s with the high-saturation colors and bold strokes of Indian Truck Art.
./Issue40/Amity Noida/A2305225427/design-notes.txt:2:The Effervescence 2025 text logo is inspired by the vibrant, dramatic visual language of 70s–80s Bollywood film posters, aligning with the Rangara theme. The typography is treated as the hero, with custom-modified letterforms rather than a standard font, ensuring originality and strong visual identity.
./Issue40/Amity Noida/A2305225427/design-notes.txt:14:The final design balances tradition and energy, creating a memorable and scalable text logo that feels festive, cinematic, and uniquely Effervescence. It is crafted to work across banners, digital media, merchandise, and promotional assets while staying true to the Rangara theme.
./README.md:12:  <b>🎭 Theme:</b> Rangara (रंगारा)<br/>
./README.md:24:And here's where it gets interesting: just like the film **Barfi** transported us back to the romantic **1970s** with its vintage aesthetics and nostalgic charm, we're diving deep into that golden era for our theme **"Rangara"** (रंगारा) - a celebration of the **colorful, dramatic, and unforgettable world of 70s-80s Bollywood!** 
